==English==
peacebuilding
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
1. The act(s) of supporting or creating peace or the conditions for peace. see http://www.cmu.ca/church-community/03_icp.html
2. The act(s) of reconstructing physical and societal institutions after a conflict. (military/UN usage) see http://www.un.org/peace/peacebuilding/
